trans-unit.source: Represents an object that identifies an item of content.
trans-unit.target: Representerer et objekt som identifiserer et element av innhold.

trans-unit.source: Derived from ContentLocatorBase, a <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.ContentLocator> identifies a data item through an ordered list of <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.ContentLocatorPart> elements.
trans-unit.target: Avledet fra ContentLocatorBase, en <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.ContentLocator>identifiserer et dataelement via en sortert liste over <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.ContentLocatorPart>elementer.</xref:System.Windows.Annotations.ContentLocatorPart> </xref:System.Windows.Annotations.ContentLocator>

trans-unit.source: Derived from ContentLocatorBase, a <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.ContentLocatorGroup> identifies a data item through a set of <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.ContentLocator> elements.
trans-unit.target: Avledet fra ContentLocatorBase, en <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.ContentLocatorGroup>identifiserer et dataelement via et sett med <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.ContentLocator>elementer.</xref:System.Windows.Annotations.ContentLocator> </xref:System.Windows.Annotations.ContentLocatorGroup>

trans-unit.source: Creates a modifiable deep copy clone of this <xref href="System.Windows.Annotations.ContentLocatorBase"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en Klon kan endres dype kopi av dette <xref href="System.Windows.Annotations.ContentLocatorBase"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: This Clone method creates modifiable copies of frozen <xref:System.Windows.Freezable> objects.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden, oppretter kan endres klone overfører for låste <xref:System.Windows.Freezable>objekter.</xref:System.Windows.Freezable>

trans-unit.source: For convenience, Clone shadows the inherited version with a strongly typed implementation.
trans-unit.target: Når som helst skygger klone arvede versjon med en forespørselsparameter av sterk type implementering.
For mer informasjon, kan du se <xref:System.Windows.Freezable.Clone%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Windows.Freezable.Clone%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The cloned <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.ContentLocatorBase>'s <xref:System.Windows.Freezable.IsFrozen%2A> property will be `false` even if this source <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.ContentLocatorBase>'s <xref:System.Windows.Freezable.IsFrozen%2A> property is `true.` When copying dependency properties, Clone copies resource references and data bindings (although they might no longer resolve) but does not copy not animations or current animation values.
trans-unit.target: Det klonede <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.ContentLocatorBase>'s <xref:System.Windows.Freezable.IsFrozen%2A>blir `false` selv om denne datakilden <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.ContentLocatorBase>'s <xref:System.Windows.Freezable.IsFrozen%2A>egenskapen `true.` når du kopierer avhengighetsegenskaper, klone overfører ressursen referanser og data bindinger (selv om de ikke kan løse), men ikke kopiere ikke animasjoner eller gjeldende animasjon-verdier.</xref:System.Windows.Freezable.IsFrozen%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Annotations.ContentLocatorBase> </xref:System.Windows.Freezable.IsFrozen%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Annotations.ContentLocatorBase>

trans-unit.source: A modifiable deep copy clone of this <xref href="System.Windows.Annotations.ContentLocatorBase"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En kopi kan endres dype kopi av denne <xref href="System.Windows.Annotations.ContentLocatorBase"> </xref>.
